53:18.996 --> 53:21.497
you made
me a promise...

53:21.599 --> 53:26.335
and it would be bad
karma to break a promise.

53:26.437 --> 53:35.911
d

53:36.013 --> 53:38.948
That's some
story, Mrs. Klint.

53:43.054 --> 53:44.954
Or should I
believe you?

53:45.056 --> 53:46.422
According to
your sister,

53:46.524 --> 53:48.591
it was her who was
in Mexico, shopping,

53:48.693 --> 53:50.826
at the time
of the murder.

53:50.928 --> 53:52.294
Yeah, look, I know
that she says that,

53:52.396 --> 53:53.796
okay, but it was
me, alright?

53:53.898 --> 53:55.397
I was the one in
Mexico and I told her

53:55.499 --> 53:57.433
everything that
happened there.

53:57.535 --> 53:59.368
Well, is
there something

53:59.470 --> 54:04.240
you can verify...
something that happened

54:04.342 --> 54:06.976
that you didn't tell
her about in Mexico?

54:07.078 --> 54:09.245
I don't know.
She told me...

54:09.347 --> 54:11.547
she had me tell her
every single detail.

54:11.649 --> 54:12.881
Okay?

54:12.984 --> 54:15.985
I didn't understand
why at the time.

54:16.087 --> 54:17.820
There's got to
be something,

54:17.922 --> 54:20.856
something that you,
um, left out.

54:25.596 --> 54:26.829
No?

54:26.931 --> 54:28.597
Look, I don't know.

54:28.699 --> 54:35.671
Well, if you do
think of something...

54:35.773 --> 54:37.606
you know
where I am.

54:37.708 --> 54:39.375
Thank you.

54:44.715 --> 54:49.351
d

54:49.453 --> 54:50.486
There was
something.

54:50.588 --> 54:52.655
Listen, there was
a police officer that

54:52.757 --> 54:54.757
stopped me on my
way back from Mexico.

54:54.859 --> 54:58.027
It was, uh, around, uh,
it was probably around

54:58.129 --> 55:00.462
the same time my dad
was being murdered.

55:00.564 --> 55:02.498
Anyway, he stopped
me to give me my-

55:02.600 --> 55:04.166
or Allie's
ID back.

55:04.268 --> 55:05.934
And then he gave me
his phone number,

55:06.037 --> 55:08.037
he told me he'd show me
around Mexico sometime

55:08.139 --> 55:09.738
and I didn't
tell her that.

55:09.840 --> 55:11.840
Okay. Does the police
officer have a name?

55:11.942 --> 55:14.576
Um, God, I didn't think
I was going to call him.

55:14.679 --> 55:18.180
Um, he was tall, he
had a southern accent.

55:18.282 --> 55:21.850
His name was, um,
Bob... Bob something.

55:21.952 --> 55:24.086
Bob?

55:24.188 --> 55:28.524
And, uh, your sister
doesn't know anything

55:28.626 --> 55:29.825
about this guy?

55:29.927 --> 55:31.093
No.

55:31.195 --> 55:33.896
Uh, she does know that
an officer stopped me,

55:33.998 --> 55:36.131
but she doesn't know
that he asked me out.

55:36.233 --> 55:38.267
I never told
her that detail.

56:23.714 --> 56:25.948
Anything?
- Nope.

56:26.050 --> 56:28.016
Whoever it is, you must
have scared him away

56:28.119 --> 56:29.685
with the
pepper spray.

56:29.787 --> 56:30.819
Okay.

56:39.830 --> 56:42.297
Um, can I offer you
something to drink?

56:42.400 --> 56:44.466
Yeah, I'll take some
coffee if you got it.

56:44.568 --> 56:45.734
Sure.

56:45.836 --> 56:47.770
By the way, I
found your cowboy.

56:47.872 --> 56:48.904
Bob Smalley.

56:49.006 --> 56:50.773
Smalley! Yes!

56:50.875 --> 56:52.841
Yes, oh, what
did he say?

56:52.943 --> 56:54.510
He verified
what you said.

56:54.612 --> 56:56.145
I told you I
was in Mexico.

56:56.247 --> 56:57.613
You believe
me now, right?

56:57.715 --> 56:59.648
I don't know, I haven't
talked to your sister yet.

56:59.750 --> 57:00.816
Well, will you?

57:00.918 --> 57:01.650
Yeah. Of course.

57:01.752 --> 57:02.985
Now?

57:03.087 --> 57:04.153
It's a
little late.

57:04.255 --> 57:05.821
Please?

57:05.923 --> 57:09.158
Alright.
Okay. Yeah.

57:09.260 --> 57:11.093
Yeah, okay.
Okay, great. Okay.

57:11.195 --> 57:12.461
Where are
you going?

57:12.563 --> 57:13.729
I'm coming
with you.

57:21.872 --> 57:23.338
Well, well,
well, detective.

57:23.441 --> 57:24.706
What do we
have here?

57:24.809 --> 57:26.775
Got yourself a new
business partner?

57:26.877 --> 57:27.776
No, ma'am.

57:27.878 --> 57:29.978
I just need to clear
a couple things up.

57:30.080 --> 57:42.391
d

57:42.493 --> 57:47.463
Miss Banks, uh, both
you and your sister say

57:47.565 --> 57:50.399
that you were in Mexico
at the time of the murder.

57:50.501 --> 57:52.768
Now I have
Miss Klint's

57:52.870 --> 57:55.437
version of events
that night.

57:55.539 --> 57:56.905
Mmm.

57:57.007 --> 57:59.808
But I'm wondering...
is there anything

57:59.910 --> 58:01.710
that you
could tell me?

58:01.812 --> 58:04.079
Maybe something that
happened down there

58:04.181 --> 58:06.315
that she doesn't
know about?

58:06.417 --> 58:10.118
Hmm. Let
me think.

58:10.221 --> 58:15.190
Um, well, there
was a rude waiter,

58:15.292 --> 58:17.559
but I think I told
her about that.

58:17.661 --> 58:19.228
What about when
you crossed back

58:19.330 --> 58:21.063
over the border?

58:21.165 --> 58:26.201
Um, a police
officer stopped me.

58:26.303 --> 58:28.337
He returned
my ID.

58:28.439 --> 58:30.572
But I told her
about that, too.

58:30.674 --> 58:36.111
And this policeman, he,
uh, do anything unusual?

58:36.213 --> 58:38.247
Unusual? No.

58:46.524 --> 58:48.590
Unless you mean
his asking me out

58:48.692 --> 58:50.826
on a date, but I
don't think there's

58:50.928 --> 58:52.861
anything unusual
about that.

58:57.902 --> 58:59.134
He gave me
his number.

58:59.236 --> 59:01.937
Told me he wanted to
show me around sometime.

59:02.039 --> 59:03.605
You know, it's so funny
that you brought him up

59:03.707 --> 59:05.974
because I just got
off the phone with Bob.

59:06.076 --> 59:08.844
That's his name.
Bob Smalley.

59:08.946 --> 59:11.547
I'm going to take
him up on his offer.

59:11.649 --> 59:13.815
We're going out
this weekend.

59:13.918 --> 59:17.185
There's just something
about policemen

59:17.288 --> 59:33.168
that I find
so appealing.

59:47.885 --> 59:49.651
Quiet. I
have a knife.

59:55.726 --> 59:57.359
I'm going to
remove my hand.

59:57.461 --> 59:59.928
Just don't scream.

01:00:08.539 --> 01:00:09.871
Sorry to scare
you that way,

01:00:09.974 --> 01:00:11.373
but I need to
talk to you.

01:00:11.475 --> 01:00:13.241
And I knew you'd
run the other way

01:00:13.344 --> 01:00:14.576
if you saw
it was me.

01:00:14.678 --> 01:00:17.145
You got me pretty bad
with the mace earlier.

01:00:17.247 --> 01:00:19.548
Look, there's some things
we gotta talk about.

01:00:19.650 --> 01:00:21.750
Man, where
do I start?

01:00:24.054 --> 01:00:25.654
That whole blackmail
thing in Texas,

01:00:25.756 --> 01:00:28.457
your sister set that
whole thing up.

01:00:28.559 --> 01:00:30.392
She cancelled your
reservation herself

01:00:30.494 --> 01:00:32.995
and she told me
just how to play it.

01:00:33.097 --> 01:00:35.998
She told me just
what you'd like.

01:00:36.100 --> 01:00:38.700
The thing is, though, she
promised me some money

01:00:38.802 --> 01:00:41.036
and now she's trying
to back out of paying.

01:00:41.138 --> 01:00:43.438
I figure with the
new developments,

01:00:43.540 --> 01:00:45.507
I got more chance
getting paid by you

01:00:45.609 --> 01:00:49.244
if I help
you out.

01:00:49.346 --> 01:00:53.415
Okay, look, I'll
pay you the money

01:00:53.517 --> 01:00:56.418
if you help me,
okay, but I just,

01:00:56.520 --> 01:00:59.888
I just need to
know why did-

01:00:59.990 --> 01:01:02.991
why did she want
you to blackmail me?

01:01:08.098 --> 01:01:10.732
She knew you didn't
have the money to pay me

01:01:10.834 --> 01:01:14.069
and that you'd do
anything to save your kid.

01:01:14.171 --> 01:01:15.937
That accidental meeting
with your friend at the

01:01:16.040 --> 01:01:17.973
restaurant was no
coincidence either.

01:01:18.075 --> 01:01:19.608
She told me she
only wanted to

01:01:19.710 --> 01:01:21.677
make up with you
and that the one way

01:01:21.779 --> 01:01:23.712
to do that was to get
you to come to her.

01:01:23.814 --> 01:01:25.247
That was the purpose
of the blackmail,

01:01:25.349 --> 01:01:27.716
to get you to come
to her for money.

01:01:27.818 --> 01:01:31.086
So my husband
never hired you.

01:01:31.188 --> 01:01:33.755
No. I never even
met your husband.

01:01:33.857 --> 01:01:36.458
He didn't have a thing
to do with any of it.

01:01:36.560 --> 01:01:38.326
It was
all Allie.

01:01:38.429 --> 01:01:41.663
She put an ad online
for an actor wanted

01:01:41.765 --> 01:01:44.099
and I answered.
Listen, hey, listen.

01:01:44.201 --> 01:01:46.635
I'm not a bad guy, but
I gotta get out of town.

01:01:46.737 --> 01:01:48.370
When I agreed to
help your sister,

01:01:48.472 --> 01:01:50.105
I didn't think anyone
was going to get hurt.

01:01:50.207 --> 01:01:51.673
I didn't know
about this whole

01:01:51.775 --> 01:01:53.141
murder thing
until after.

01:01:53.243 --> 01:01:54.476
You helped
murder my dad?

01:01:54.578 --> 01:01:55.644
No!

01:01:55.746 --> 01:02:00.048
No way. I helped
her with her alibi.

01:02:00.150 --> 01:02:03.552
I planted the video
cameras in the two hats.

01:02:03.654 --> 01:02:08.690
Video cameras?
In the hats?

01:02:08.792 --> 01:02:12.294
That's what I
was smuggling.

01:02:12.396 --> 01:02:15.163
No, no, no, no.

01:02:15.265 --> 01:02:17.199
There was
no smuggling.

01:02:17.301 --> 01:02:22.604
It was just a way for her
to be two places at once.

01:02:22.706 --> 01:02:27.509
So she had an alibi
and I had nothing.

01:02:27.611 --> 01:02:30.278
And that's how
she knew...

01:02:30.380 --> 01:02:32.781
That's how she knew
about everything.

01:02:32.883 --> 01:02:37.352
Even the things
that I didn't tell her.

01:02:37.454 --> 01:02:38.787
Oh my, God.

01:02:38.889 --> 01:02:40.756
You know what?
Like it or not,

01:02:40.858 --> 01:02:42.324
you are working
for me now.

01:02:49.600 --> 01:02:52.701
Okay, that's all the
money I have right now.

01:02:52.803 --> 01:02:54.536
I'll pay you the
rest after you

01:02:54.638 --> 01:02:56.071
come with me
to the police.

01:02:56.173 --> 01:02:58.039
Whoa! No!
No police.

01:02:58.142 --> 01:02:59.107
Okay, then.

01:02:59.209 --> 01:03:02.010
Okay. Look,
I'll help you,

01:03:02.112 --> 01:03:06.214
I just can't
go to the cops.

01:03:06.316 --> 01:03:08.617
I'm still
on probation.

01:03:08.719 --> 01:03:14.089
And Allie still has
the original of this.

01:03:14.191 --> 01:03:16.324
It's the tape she
made of that little

01:03:16.426 --> 01:03:19.227
blackmail episode
in the park.

01:03:19.329 --> 01:03:21.096
But that's perfect.
That's-that's the proof

01:03:21.198 --> 01:03:23.131
that at least part
of my story is true.

01:03:23.233 --> 01:03:24.800
Sorry, I can't
let you have it.

01:03:24.902 --> 01:03:28.236
It could land me
in jail again,

01:03:28.338 --> 01:03:30.205
this time
for blackmail.

01:03:30.307 --> 01:03:34.075
But that was all part
of her setup. Right?

01:03:34.178 --> 01:03:35.744
You were just
acting, Harry.

01:03:35.846 --> 01:03:38.246
It was still
blackmail.

01:03:38.348 --> 01:03:41.583
That tape doesn't
really prove much anyway.

01:03:41.685 --> 01:03:45.153
Not about
the murder.

01:03:45.255 --> 01:03:47.556
Listen, if Allie still
trusts you I need you to

01:03:47.658 --> 01:03:49.558
get something about
the murder on tape.

01:03:49.660 --> 01:03:51.459
Okay? Just get
her to admit it.

01:03:51.562 --> 01:03:55.864
It can't hurt to try.
I'm seeing her soon.

01:03:55.966 --> 01:03:58.600
But like I said,
it'll cost you.

01:03:58.702 --> 01:04:02.437
Okay.

01:04:02.539 --> 01:04:05.473
Okay, I'll get
you the money.

01:04:05.576 --> 01:04:07.309
I even know where I
can get one of those

01:04:07.411 --> 01:04:09.477
nanny cams on
short notice.

01:04:09.580 --> 01:04:14.482
Harry... thank
you so much.

01:04:14.585 --> 01:04:16.451
Listen, thank you.

01:04:16.553 --> 01:04:19.120
Thank you so much
for all of this.

01:04:19.223 --> 01:04:22.724
I knew you were a
better person than this.

01:04:22.826 --> 01:04:38.773
d

01:04:39.676 --> 01:04:41.443
I really appreciate
this, Maddie.

01:04:41.545 --> 01:04:43.511
I hope you're not too
late for your date.

01:04:43.614 --> 01:04:45.847
Oh, pfft, it's not a
problem. Just a sec.

01:04:45.949 --> 01:04:47.849
Let me grab it
from upstairs.

01:04:54.858 --> 01:04:55.991
This was
really helpful

01:04:56.093 --> 01:04:57.959
getting me feedback
on my listings

01:04:58.061 --> 01:05:00.662
until I found
out it's illegal.

01:05:00.764 --> 01:05:02.664
Okay, great.
Where's the camera?

01:05:02.766 --> 01:05:03.965
It's in its eyes.

01:05:04.067 --> 01:05:06.368
It actually records
straight to an SD card.

01:05:06.470 --> 01:05:07.502
Perfect.

01:05:07.604 --> 01:05:08.770
Thank you,
Maddie.

01:05:08.872 --> 01:05:10.505
Yeah, you
got it.

01:05:10.607 --> 01:05:12.540
Harry: Come
on, let's go.

01:05:12.643 --> 01:05:15.810
Are you sure you
can trust this guy?

01:05:15.913 --> 01:05:17.712
No...

01:05:17.814 --> 01:05:20.181
I don't really
have another choice.

01:05:20.284 --> 01:05:24.719
Um, listen, I-
I got this.

01:05:24.821 --> 01:05:26.855
It's a recording of that
whole blackmail thing

01:05:26.957 --> 01:05:28.456
in the park.

01:05:28.558 --> 01:05:29.724
Okay.

01:05:29.826 --> 01:05:31.559
Harry: Hey,
come on.

01:05:41.838 --> 01:05:43.038
Okay,
here it is.

01:05:43.140 --> 01:05:44.906
You'll bring it by my
house when you're done?

01:05:45.008 --> 01:05:46.107
Okay.

01:06:13.670 --> 01:06:14.502
You're late.

01:06:14.604 --> 01:06:15.870
Hey, doll.

01:06:19.476 --> 01:06:21.576
That's 'cause I stopped
to buy you something.

01:06:21.678 --> 01:06:23.278
A little gift.

01:06:23.380 --> 01:06:24.579
That?

01:06:24.681 --> 01:06:25.847
Does this look
like something

01:06:25.949 --> 01:06:27.916
that I
would like?

01:06:28.018 --> 01:06:29.417
Give me a
break, Allie.

01:06:29.519 --> 01:06:30.785
I thought
it was cute.

01:06:30.887 --> 01:06:32.554
Then you
keep it.

01:06:36.727 --> 01:06:39.294
Come on, Allie...

01:06:39.396 --> 01:06:42.197
He's cute.

01:06:42.299 --> 01:06:44.332
I thought you could
name him after me.

01:06:49.106 --> 01:06:52.040
So why did you have to
see me tonight, hmm?

01:06:52.142 --> 01:06:54.642
If it's about the money,
I don't have it yet.

01:06:54.745 --> 01:06:56.411
No, baby, I
missed you.

01:06:56.513 --> 01:06:58.913
You've been
so busy lately.

01:06:59.016 --> 01:07:01.416
Yes, I have had a
lot on my mind.

01:07:01.518 --> 01:07:03.985
Yeah, this murder
thing, I know.

01:07:04.087 --> 01:07:05.820
Oh, you do,
do you? Hmm?

01:07:05.922 --> 01:07:07.889
No, not
all of it.

01:07:07.991 --> 01:07:11.459
You never told me who
was in on it with you.

01:07:11.561 --> 01:07:15.096
Well, I already told you
more than you should know.

01:07:15.198 --> 01:07:17.499
But you're just
such a damn good lay.

01:07:24.408 --> 01:07:27.008
Thank you so
much for coming.

01:07:27.110 --> 01:07:28.510
I knew you'd
believe me.

01:07:28.612 --> 01:07:29.844
Actually,
I don't.

01:07:29.946 --> 01:07:32.247
Honestly, this
whole thing sounds

01:07:32.349 --> 01:07:33.948
pretty farfetched.

01:07:34.051 --> 01:07:37.786
Fake blackmail,
cameras in hats.

01:07:37.888 --> 01:07:39.354
I know, but it's
the truth, okay?

01:07:39.456 --> 01:07:41.189
And I can prove it
to you and I will.

01:07:41.291 --> 01:07:42.690
He'll-he'll
be here soon.

01:07:42.793 --> 01:07:44.559
I don't think
he's coming.

01:07:44.661 --> 01:07:46.327
No, please.

01:07:46.430 --> 01:07:47.996
It's late.

01:07:48.098 --> 01:07:49.330
Could you
just wait? I...

01:07:49.433 --> 01:07:50.498
I'm sorry.

01:07:52.335 --> 01:07:55.103
Hold on,
this is him.

01:07:55.205 --> 01:07:57.105
Hi, Jess. I guess by
now you've figured out

01:07:57.207 --> 01:07:58.807
I wasn't
coming over.

01:07:58.909 --> 01:08:00.875
Sorry, but I felt the
need to leave town fast.

01:08:00.977 --> 01:08:03.078
Oh, and, uh, thanks for
that money you gave me,

01:08:03.180 --> 01:08:04.846
by the way. It's gonna
come in real handy.

01:08:04.948 --> 01:08:06.948
Honestly, I don't think
your plan to frame Allie

01:08:07.050 --> 01:08:08.716
would have worked.
No one would believe

01:08:08.819 --> 01:08:10.718
that story
we concocted.

01:08:10.821 --> 01:08:12.520
But, hey, it was
great knowing you.

01:08:12.622 --> 01:08:14.089
And I hope you
get away with it.

01:08:14.191 --> 01:08:15.657
Oh, and here's
some footage of us

01:08:15.759 --> 01:08:17.692
from last night to
remember me by.

01:08:23.332 --> 01:08:24.732
Oh, God, no.

01:08:24.835 --> 01:08:26.533
That-that
wasn't last night.

01:08:26.636 --> 01:08:28.269
And everything
he said is a lie.

01:08:28.371 --> 01:08:29.437
Everything
is a lie.

01:08:29.538 --> 01:08:31.238
So you didn't pay him
to frame your sister?

01:08:31.341 --> 01:08:35.710
No! I-I did pay him,
but it wasn't like that.

01:08:35.812 --> 01:08:36.845
Please,
believe me.

01:08:36.947 --> 01:08:39.214
I- Look, that video was
actually from Texas and

01:08:39.316 --> 01:08:42.649
it proves actually that
I was telling the truth.

01:08:42.752 --> 01:08:45.319
No, what it does is it
proves you're lying.

01:08:45.421 --> 01:08:47.154
It proves that you
and him were in on it

01:08:47.256 --> 01:08:48.756
from the beginning
to kill your father

01:08:48.859 --> 01:08:50.091
and frame
your sister.

01:08:50.193 --> 01:08:52.493
No. I just...
I just...

01:08:52.595 --> 01:08:55.296
let me think.
I just, um...

01:08:55.398 --> 01:08:56.798
There's
another tape.

01:08:56.899 --> 01:08:57.932
Oh.

01:08:58.033 --> 01:08:59.767
It was- Maddie made
it in the park

