01:19:03.773 --> 01:19:06.674
It's the money
or the cops.

01:19:06.776 --> 01:19:09.343
Yeah?

01:19:09.445 --> 01:19:11.679
<i>I have Allesandra</i>
<i> Banks in the lobby.</i>

01:19:11.781 --> 01:19:13.247
Send her in.

01:19:20.890 --> 01:19:24.325
