to blackmail us.

01:19:24.427 --> 01:19:26.761
She has a copy of
the cassette tape.

01:19:26.863 --> 01:19:28.095
How much does
she want?

01:19:28.197 --> 01:19:29.663
It doesn't matter. The
more I think about it

01:19:29.766 --> 01:19:31.732
I don't think it
proves anything.

01:19:31.834 --> 01:19:33.801
